msgid "data foo = bar | baz\n"
msgstr "data foo = bar | baz\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/DataTypes.md:240
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The same goes for similar data definitions like records and sum types\n"
"(both will be explained below):\n"
